Note: Only auto attacks can critically strike, but Slowbro has 0% base Critical-Hit rate at all levels.

Slowpoke

Evolves At 4

Oblivious

Passive Ability

Slowbro stores up lost HP for a short time (blue HP). Slowbro's Oblivious health remains for 6s and then decreases by 3% max HP every second. When dealing damage to an enemy with Water Gun, Scald, Surf, or Slowbeam - decrease their Sp.Def by 4% for 5s, stacking up to 5 times.

Attack

Auto Attack

Becomes a boosted attack with every third attack. When this boosted attack hits, deal damage to nearby enemies and decrease their movement speed by 30% for 1s.

100% Atk + 0 x (Level - 1) + 0

110% SpA + 9 x (Level - 1) + 180

Water Gun

Move 1

5.00s Ranged

Slowbro fires a stream of water, damaging and slowing enemies hit by 35% for 1s. This move can be channeled to increase its range and damage. Slowbro's movement speed is reduced while channeling. Restore some of Slowbro's Oblivious health (blue HP) once, after hitting an enemy.

147% SpA + 13 x (Level - 1) + 240

196% SpA + 17 x (Level - 1) + 320

245% SpA + 22 x (Level - 1) + 400

294% SpA + 26 x (Level - 1) + 480

Water Gun Upgrade Choices

Scald

5.00s Ranged

Slowbro fires a stream of boiling water; damaging enemies hit, slowing them by 80% for 0.5s and creating a cloud of steam centered on the first enemy hit, which slows by 30% for 3s and applies a burn to all enemies inside. This burn reduces Attack by 60% for 3s. Restore 10% of Slowbro's Oblivious health (blue HP) once per stream instance after hitting an enemy (maximum 3 times).

100% SpA + 7 x (Level - 1) + 160

20% SpA + 1 x (Level - 1) + 32

Increases the size of the steam cloud.

Surf

7.00s Hindrance

Slowbro rides on a wave, damaging, knocking enemies back, and throwing them in the air for .4s. Two more waves follow after the first, damaging and slowing enemies by 25% for 1s. Restore 10% of Slowbro's Oblivious health (blue HP) per wave, when hitting at least one enemy (maximum 3 times).

103% SpA + 6 x (Level - 1) + 210

The second and third waves will now also throw enemies in the air for .75s, and the second wave will knock them back.

Slack Off

Move 2

11.00s Recovery

Slowbro begins channeling a nap and gains a heal over time, healing 2% max HP every 0.5s for 3s. While Slowbro remains channeling its nap, all self-healing is doubled (including Slack Off healing). Slowbro can be manually or forcibly woken up from their nap.

Slack Off Upgrade Choices

Amnesia

9.00s Recovery

Slowbro briefly becomes unstoppable, gaining +250 Defense for 4s and restoring 17.5% of Slowbro's Oblivious health (blue HP) every second for 4s.

Also increases Slowbro's Sp. Defense by 125.

Telekinesis

7.50s Hindrance

Slowbro shoots a beam, causing the first enemy hit to float in the air for 2.3s, restoring 15% of Slowbro's Oblivious health (blue HP) every second for 5s. Slowbro can reactivate the ability to pull the enemy to themself, but otherwise cannot act for the duration.

Increases the range and speed of the beam.

Slowbeam

Unite Move

112s 100000 Hindrance

Unlocks at level 9

Stare at an enemy and attack continually, dealing damage every .5 seconds for 3s and applying 'Bound' to them. This ability counters Unstoppable. Grants a shield (10% max HP) and makes Slowbro unstoppable while using this move.

80% SpA + 3 x (Level - 1) + 170

Unite Buffs (6s duration):

30% Movement Speed, 40% Max HP Shield
